---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import "tailwindcss";
---

<Layout title="VashonMesh - Community Mesh Networks">
  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <h1>VashonMesh</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Connecting Vashon & Maury Islanders <br/>...with Local Mesh Networks</p>
      
    </section>

    <section class="content">
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Welcome</h2>
        <p>
          VashonMesh is a small group of rebels informally helping islanders connect with MeshCore and
          related local area mesh networks.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our mission is to empower neighbors to build resilient, decentralized networks that
          foster communication and collaboration.
        </p>
        <a href="about"><span class="rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-sm whitespace-nowrap text-purple-700">
  About Us
</span></a>

      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>What is Mesh Networking?</h2>
        <p>
          Mesh networks enable direct, peer-to-peer connections between devices, creating
          resilient communication systems that don't rely on traditional internet infrastructure: no cell towers, no subscriptions, inexpensive radios without license requirements, and better range than FRMS walkie-talkies.
          </p>
        <p>
          Read more about <a href="https://meshcore.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LoRa (Long Range) Technology</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2>Get Involved</h2>
        <p>
          Interested in joining or learning more about local mesh networks? 
          We are all learning and experimenting. Join with us to learn more!
        </p>
        <a href="join"><span class="rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-sm whitespace-nowrap text-purple-700">How to Participate!</span></a>

      </div>

            <div class="card">
        <h2>Get a Radio</h2>
        <p>
          Interested in how to get started? 
          We're here to help you get connected.
        </p>
      </div>

                  <div class="card">
        <h2>Set up a Neighborhood Repeater</h2>
        <p>
          Ensure your neighborhood has great connectivity. 
          We're here to help you get connected.
        </p>
      </div>

            </div>
            <div class="card">
        <h2>Current Activities</h2>
        <p>
          See what we've been up to and how you can participate!
        </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  main {
    margin: auto;
    padding: 1rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .card h2 {
    color: #667eea;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .card p {
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
